# MediaCore Python

- Python `>=3.12`, manage deps with `uv`, config in root `pyproject.toml`.
- Prefer `packages.*` imports over legacy `extractor.*` shims.
- Domain errors: `packages.core.exceptions.MediaCoreError` subclasses with `code`.
- Settings: `packages.config.settings` (API re-exports via `apps.api.config`).
- Auth helpers: `packages.auth` (API re-exports via `apps.api.security`).
- Tests: `uv run pytest`; use markers (`unit`, `api`, `provider`, …). Prefer `packages.testkit` contracts.
- After provider catalog changes: `uv run python scripts/sync_platform_catalog.py --offline`.
- Keep modules focused; avoid drive-by refactors unrelated to the task.
